text: Baja Prog is an annual progressive rock festival in Mexicali, Baja California, Mexico, held since 1997. It draws a number of well-known bands in the genre, and an average of 1500 attendees each day. ==References== * * ==External links== * Official site * Bands - 2007 * Schedule - 2007 * Category:Festivals in Mexicali Category:Music festivals established in 1997 Category:Rock festivals in Mexico Category:Tourist attractions in Baja California
